ca.ualberta.cs.team1travelexpenseapp

Class MultiSelectionSpinner

  • java.lang.Object
    • Spinner
      • ca.ualberta.cs.team1travelexpenseapp.MultiSelectionSpinner

  • public class MultiSelectionSpinner
extends Spinner
    Implements a "MultiSelectionSpinner", when clicked it presents a dialog allowing for selection of a subset of items from a list using checkboxes. Selected items will then show as a comma separated list on the face of the spinner. The methods allow setting and getting of the selected items, as well as the entire list of possible items. It can store an arrayList of arbitrary objects in order to recover the selected objects directly.
